OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FThe UK's Eurovision entrant Look Mum
OL,8,FNo Computer is to perform in the grand
OL,9,Ffinal of the Eurovision Song Contest
OL,10,Fon Saturday, alongside Israel's Noam
OL,11,FBettan, after the country's inclusion
OL,12,Fin the competition prompted a boycott
OL,13,Fby five nations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
