FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FLook Mum No Computer, whose real name
OL,8,Fis Sam Battle, will perform on
OL,9,FSaturday at the Wiener Stadthalle in
OL,10,FVienna, Austria, having sung in
OL,11,FThursday's semi-final despite already
OL,12,Fqualifying as one of the big four
OL,13,Falongside France, Italy and Germany,
OL,14,Fwho contribute the most to Eurovision
OL,15,Ffinancially.
OL,17,FAustria's entrant, Cosmo, also
OL,18,Freceived automatic qualification as
OL,19,Fthe host nation, after Austria's JJ
OL,20,Fwon the 2025 contest with his song
OL,21,FWasted Love.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FBattle, who will perform 14th in the
OL,8,Frunning order at the final, is best
OL,9,Fknown for his YouTube career, which
OL,10,Fbegan in 2013.
OL,12,FHe makes his own quirky musical
OL,13,Finstruments, including an organ from
OL,14,FFurby toys and a triple oscillator
OL,15,Fsynthesiser made out of Nintendo Game
OL,16,FBoy consoles.
OL,18,FIsraeli entrant Bettan, 28, was booed
OL,19,Fby the crowd during his performance in
OL,20,FTuesday's semi-final. He will perform
OL,21,Fthird in Saturday's event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FBettan received a mixed reception from
OL,8,Fthe crowd before his performance
OL,9,Fbegan, with some members of the
OL,10,Faudience shouting, and later booing,
OL,11,Fduring the quiet moments of his song
OL,12,FMichelle.
OL,14,FThere were a number of protests in the
OL,15,FAustrian capital this week over
OL,16,FIsrael's inclusion in the contest amid
OL,17,Fits actions in Gaza. Ireland, Iceland,
OL,18,Fthe Netherlands, Spain and Slovenia
OL,19,Fhave boycotted the event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FThe largest protest was the No Stage
OL,8,FFor Genocide event, organised by
OL,9,FPalestine Solidarity Austria, which
OL,10,Ftook place at Venediger Au, a playpark
OL,11,Fon the outskirts of Vienna, which was
OL,12,Fattended by hundreds of supporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FMarco Wanjura, part of the team
OL,8,Forganising the event, told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "The European Song
OL,10,FContest claims to stand for
OL,11,Fsolidarity, love, diversity, and
OL,12,Feverything, but in reality, this
OL,13,Fyear's contest is hosting Israel as a
OL,14,Fcountry which is right now committing
OL,15,Fa genocide in Gaza.
OL,17,F"And that's why we wanted to show that
OL,18,Fthe majority in Austria is actually
OL,19,Fagainst that."
OL,26,@qD@NOUyD@AOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
