PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FEarlier this week, human rights group
OL,8,FAmnesty International criticised the
OL,9,FEuropean Broadcasting Union (EBU) for
OL,10,Fits failure to suspend Israel from the
OL,11,Fsong contest, as it did with Russia
OL,12,Fafter its full-scale invasion of
OL,13,FUkraine in 2022, calling it an act of
OL,14,F"cowardice" and a "blatant double
OL,15,Fstandard".
OL,17,FIsrael's 2025 entrant Yuval Raphael
OL,18,Freceived the largest number of votes
OL,19,Ffrom the public last May, ultimately
OL,20,Ffinishing runner-up to JJ after the
OL,21,Fjury votes were taken into account.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@KO]vD@SOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
