FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FTwo protesters unsuccessfully
OL,8,Fattempted to storm the stage and throw
OL,9,Fpaint during her performance last year.
OL,11,FLook Mum No Computer will not be the
OL,12,Fonly British-born performer in the
OL,13,Ffinal. Former Love Island contestant
OL,14,FAntigoni, full name Antigoni Buxton,
OL,15,Fwill perform her song Jalla for Cyprus.
OL,17,FAntigoni competed in the eighth series
OL,18,Fof the reality TV show in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FVeteran British pop star Boy George
OL,8,Fwas also involved in the competition,
OL,9,Fbut was eliminated in the first semi-
OL,10,Ffinal on Tuesday, having joined San
OL,11,FMarino's entrant Senhit to perform the
OL,12,Fsong Superstar, which he co-wrote.
OL,14,FAnother famous face for British
OL,15,Faudiences will be Australia's entrant,
OL,16,Fformer Neighbours star Delta Goodrem,
OL,17,Fwho will sing her song Eclipse. She
OL,18,Fhad top 10 hits in the UK with songs
OL,19,Fincluding Lost Without You, Born To
OL,20,FTry and Innocent Eyes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FDuring Goodrem's eye-catching
OL,8,Fperformance she is lifted into the air
OL,9,Ffrom the top of a golden piano, while
OL,10,Fquirky acts will include Greece's
OL,11,FAkylas, whose performance of Ferto
OL,12,Fwill feature video game-inspired
OL,13,Fstaging during which he travels
OL,14,Fthrough a tunnel and eventually ends
OL,15,Fup in a tiger-print house.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FRomania's Alexandra Capitanescu will
OL,8,Fdraw attention with her performance of
OL,9,Fpop metal song Choke Me, during which
OL,10,Fshe sings while attached to her band
OL,11,Fvia illuminated wires; and Lithuania's
OL,12,FLion Ceccah, who begins his
OL,13,Fperformance painted silver in a grim
OL,14,Freaper-style costume.
OL,16,FThe final will open with a performance
OL,17,Ffrom last year's winner JJ, and there
OL,18,Fwill also be a medley of classic
OL,19,FEurovision songs to celebrate the
OL,20,Fcompetition's 70th anniversary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778918777
OL,3,CLook Mum No Computer to perform in
OL,4,CEurovision final amid boycott over
OL,5,CIsrael
OL,7,FThe competing countries in the grand
OL,8,Ffinal will be Albania, Australia,
OL,9,FAustria, Belgium, Bulgaria, Croatia,
OL,10,FCyprus, Czechia, Denmark, Finland,
OL,11,FFrance, Germany, Greece, Israel,
OL,12,FItaly, Lithuania, Malta, Moldova,
OL,13,FNorway, Poland, Romania, Serbia,
OL,14,FSweden, Ukraine and the UK.
OL,16,FThe Eurovision Song Contest grand
OL,17,Ffinal will take place on Saturday at
OL,18,F8pm, and will be shown live on BBC One
OL,19,Fand BBC iPlayer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
